Published for the American Vacuum Society by the American Institute of Physics. Soft cover. 8vo (imperial). Near Fine. Item #003744

[1984. N.p.] A special volume commemorating the 30th anniversary of the American Vacuum Society, 1953-1983. Original cream card wraps, sewn and glued binding. vii, 168 p.p. Illustrated in B&W. Bruising to spine head and fore edge of front cover.
